# Cal.com booking link for the contact section, as `username/event-slug`.
# Create a free account at https://cal.com, add an event type (e.g. a 30-minute
# intro call), then use the part of its URL after cal.com/ — for example:
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_CAL_LINK=tayyab/30min
#
# Public by design: it is the same identifier as your public cal.com URL, so it
# is safe to expose in the client bundle, hence NEXT_PUBLIC_.
#
# Copy this file to .env.local for local development, and set the same variable
# in your host's environment settings (e.g. Vercel → Project → Settings →
# Environment Variables) for production.
NEXT_PUBLIC_CAL_LINK=
